data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 5 bedroom NE Home! This versatile floor plan is great for all! Offering 2 living spaces, a huge primary suite, and an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances. The home has been updated recently with New Tile flooring, new light fixtures throughout the home, and a front security gate. Some other recent updates include newer vinyl windows, TPO Roof, and remodeled bathrooms. And that is not all! This home also has backyard access, a two car carport, and refrigerated air to keep you cool in the summer! Topping it all off with a stunner 16x16 workshop and two sheds that provide a ton of storage/work space! Don't let this one get away!
